{"tid":379211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛頭角道爆水管　馬路成黃河","createTime":"2017-08-29T06:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T07:21:51.000Z","uid":131622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45789c54f0b916f92624a93a020004b193888592","tid":379211,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:29:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/bkn-20170829132544439-0829_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170829%2Fbkn-20170829132544439-0829_00822_001.html&d=BhjIpfkjzNmk%2F6yVm3sc18mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4a470fb7\" target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/bkn-20170829132544439-0829_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n牛頭角有地底水管爆裂。現場為牛頭角道77號淘大花園對開，下午1時許，地底有水管突爆裂，大量黃泥水混合沙石湧出地面，馬路及行人路頓成澤國，行人要涉水而行。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，牛頭角道往觀塘方向慢線需要封閉，交通受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/142842_27ea5e399599d06b4544bad2a36fc719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F142842_27ea5e399599d06b4544bad2a36fc719.jpg&h=10de4738&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"317939a8400d151c49f9534358a949f7ff1d4a0a","tid":379211,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"有冇喺現場附近嘅巴打知道而家情況點？"},{"pid":"68cdd733f00f0f4018e9a0f95cd6182e7a289822","tid":379211,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇喺現場附近嘅巴打知道而家情況點？</blockquote><br />\nd水退得七七八八 不過附近停哂水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ef2198fd668fb9de0f943151d798c896c48d02","tid":379211,"uid":134039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/152013_ef2c03d4d2c5c93a1ee47a05e9983e3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn